      "notes": ""
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "preheat grill to 400f",
    "in a large bowl, whisk together lemon juice, olive oil, garlic, salt, black pepper, and paprika",
    "add lamb cubes to the bowl and toss to coat",
    "thread lamb cubes onto skewers, leaving a little space between each cube",
    "grill kebabs for 8 minutes per side, or until lamb is cooked through",
    "transfer kebabs to a plate and let rest for 5 minutes",
    "garnish with chopped parsley and serve",
    "optional: steam kebabs for 5 minutes before serving to add extra moisture and flavor"
  ],
